14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 68 O.S. 2021, Section 4503, is
15 amended to read as follows:
16 Section 4503. A. As used in the Oklahoma Remote Quality Jobs
17 Incentive Act:
18 1. "Basic industry" means an establishment that attracts remote
19 workers to the state whose purpose is to increase the state's
20 population and who may receive rebates on the remote workers
21 provided that the remote workers meet the wage and health insurance
22 requirements in state and provide evidence of such to the proxy
23 establishment;
